author: David Ng
title: Woody Harrelson Among Celebs Sharing Conspiracy Theory Linking Coronavirus to 5G
description: Actor Woody Harrelson and the rapper known as M.I.A are among a growing number of people sharing a conspiracy theory that links the spread of the coronavirus with 5G wireless technology.
